body:
> Different across different graphdefs?

No, it is different across the same files. if anything was different across two files (where it generates A and B), I was detecting it in the previous step with the code. All files are identical.

`seed` and `seed2` are written in two places in a file and `seed2` value, as I wrote above, has two values in the file, but as you see `seed` is fixed to `1234` in both
